Note: ═══════════════════════════════════
Note: EPL Power Test 3: Math & Logic
Note: ═══════════════════════════════════

Note: Collatz conjecture (3n+1 problem)
Function collatz takes n
    steps = 0
    While n != 1
        If n % 2 == 0 then
            n = n / 2
        Otherwise
            n = n * 3 + 1
        End
        steps = steps + 1
    End
    Return steps
End

Print "Collatz steps:"
For i from 1 to 20
    Print collatz(i)
End

Note: ─────────────────────────────────

Note: Triangle numbers
Function triangle takes n
    Return n * (n + 1) / 2
End

Print "Triangle numbers:"
For i from 1 to 10
    Print triangle(i)
End

Note: ─────────────────────────────────

Note: Absolute value
Function abs takes x
    If x < 0 then
        Return 0 - x
    End
    Return x
End

Print "Absolute values:"
Print abs(42)
Print abs(0 - 17)
Print abs(0)

Note: ─────────────────────────────────

Note: Complex conditions
x = 42
If x > 10 then
    If x > 20 then
        If x > 40 then
            Print "x is very big"
        Otherwise
            Print "x is medium-big"
        End
    Otherwise
        Print "x is smallish"
    End
Otherwise
    Print "x is small"
End

Note: ─────────────────────────────────

Note: Sum of digits
Function digitSum takes n
    sum = 0
    While n > 0
        sum = sum + n % 10
        n = n / 10
    End
    Return sum
End

Print "Digit sums:"
Print digitSum(123)
Print digitSum(9999)
Print digitSum(12345)

Note: ─────────────────────────────────

Note: Compute series: 1 + 1/2 + 1/3 + ... + 1/n (as integer sum)
Note: (harmonic-like integer version)
Function harmonicInt takes n
    total = 0
    For i from 1 to n
        Increase total by 1000 / i
    End
    Return total
End

Print "Harmonic(10) x1000:"
Print harmonicInt(10)
Print "Harmonic(100) x1000:"
Print harmonicInt(100)

Print "All math tests passed!"
